<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Konrad von Kochberg, Vogt zu Coburg, und Rat Coburgs</head><p>Der Rat bittet für Peter Tafler, Bürger zu Nürnberg, um Anweisung des Hans Karl, Bürger zu Coburg, weitere Schreiben zu unterlassen, weil man ihm den Rechtsweg nie versagt hat.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_59" id="28r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_59_r1l3"><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> von Kochberg 
<add><ab facs="#facs_59_r1l1">Amptman </ab></add> vnd den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l5">Burgern des Rats der Stat cʒu <expan>Kob<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_59_r1l8">Lıeber her Conrad / vnd <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freunde / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_59_line_1574240674709_1076">Vns </ab></add>
<add><ab facs="#facs_59_line_1592288195037_265">
<del rend="strikethrough">Eʒ </del></ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vns </del> hat hans Karl </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l9">Burger 
<del rend="strikethrough"> c </del> ʒu Koburg / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> vns </del> einen brief geſant / vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> auch </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l10">dem Peter Tafler <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Burger auch einen / als wir ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l11">der abſchrift ſenden hirynne <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> / Nu dunckt vns ſölch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l12"><expan>verſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gar <expan>vncʒimlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein von <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l13"><expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> / vvir Jm von dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Burger 
<del rend="strikethrough"> nẏe khein </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_59_line_1574240817810_1093">des </ab></add> rehten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_line_1592288275999_299">
<add>cʒu <expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan> nẏe</add> verſagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Darümb <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l15">den <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> Burger daran weẏſen wöllet / daʒ Er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l16">ſich ſölchs ſchreẏbens v̈berhebe / vnd hab Er cʒu dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l17"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> Burger icht cʒuſprechen / daʒ Er oder ſein ſcheinbote </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l21">
<add><ab facs="#facs_59_line_1576657304370_3754">mit <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_59_line_1576657307423_3759">gewalte </ab></add> das hie vorder 
<add><ab facs="#facs_59_line_1574240920448_1123">mit <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>euntlichen</ex></expan> <expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> So wollen wir Jm <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l24">cʒum rehten ſtellen / vnd Jm <expan>vörderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des rechten von Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l26">helffen nach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat reht 
<add><ab facs="#facs_59_r1l25">ongeuerde </ab></add> vnd getrawen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l28">wol / daʒ Jr Jm 
<del rend="strikethrough">des fürbaʒ </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_59_r1l27">ſolchs ſchreıbens </ab></add> nıht mer geſtatet / Das wöllen 
<del rend="strikethrough">e </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l29">wir v̈mb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> / <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> freuntlich <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_59_r1l30"><expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> lat vns darümb wıder wiſſen beẏ diſem boten </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_59" id="28r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> von Kochberg, <add>amptman</add>, und den
                        burgern des rats der stat czu <expan>Kob<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber her Conrad und <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> freunde, <add>uns</add>
                        hat Hans Karl, burger zu Koburg, einen brief gesant und dem Peter Tafler,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> burger, auch einen, als wir ew der
                        abschrift senden hirynne <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan>. Nu dunckt uns
                        sölch <expan>verschreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gar
                            <expan>unczimlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein von
                            <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir im von dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
                        burger, <add>des</add> rehten <add>czu <expan>helffe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                            nye</add> versagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Darümb
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen den
                            <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        burger, daran weysen wöllet, daz er sich sölchs schreybens überhebe, und hab
                        er czu dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
                        burger, icht czusprechen, daz er oder sein scheinbote <add>mit
                                    <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalte</add> das hie vorder <add>mit
                                    <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>euntlichen</ex></expan>
<expan>rehte<ex>n</ex></expan></add>, so wollen wir im
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> czum rehten stellen und im
                                <expan>vörderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des rechten von im helffen nach
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> stat reht <add>ongeverde</add> und
                        getrawen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit wol, daz ir im <add>solchs
                            schreibens</add> niht mer gestatet. Das wöllen wir ümb
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Ew<ex>r</ex></expan> freuntlich
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> lat uns darümb wider wissen bey disem
                        boten.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
